2. Email
tonielrosoft@gmail.com
We will repond to your complaint as soon as we receive your email.
4. Updates to this Policy
We will update this Privacy Policy from time to time. These updates, will take effect from the date of issue on our website at tonielrosoft.com. Please check back regularly for updates.
